    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# scope-of-work model structures deliverables and milestones\n\n`powerhouse/scope-of-work` (33 ops) is the third-largest model by operation count. Structures project deliverables, milestones, timelines, and budget allocations. Part of the Work Management zone.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- May reference [[builder-profile model describes individual contributor identities]] for assignees\n- May feed into [[invoice model generates formal payment requests]] for milestone-based billing\n- Related to [[request-for-proposals model manages procurement workflows]] (RFP \u2192 awarded SoW)\n- [[workstream model organizes ongoing work streams]] may group multiple scopes\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nWork Management zone. High operation count (33) suggests complex deliverable management with nested line items.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
    }
  },
